打了一个小时的电话给你
Been calling you for like an hour.

163
00:11:10,936 --> 00:11:12,904
我以为这样你就明白了
I thought you'd have taken the hint.

164
00:11:16,042 --> 00:11:18,237
爱格妮丝死后你就一直这样浑浑噩噩的
You've been acting like this
since Agnes was killed.

165
00:11:18,411 --> 00:11:19,878
可不，但能怪我吗？
Yeah. Can you blame me?

166
00:11:20,046 --> 00:11:23,106
最近又没多少事可做
It's not like I have a lot
to keep me going these days.

167
00:11:24,583 --> 00:11:26,278
当你随便找个大街上的人
While you've been
drowning your sorrows

168
00:11:26,452 --> 00:11:28,647
来抚平内心悲痛的时候
by nailing everything that walks,

169
00:11:28,821 --> 00:11:32,917
我一直在四处观察
低调行事，打探消息
I've been doing my tours,
keeping my head down and my ears open.

170
00:11:33,092 --> 00:11:37,256
马赛尔的日行者正在全城上下
找一个女孩
Marcel's Daywalkers are scouring
the whole town looking for a girl,

171
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:40,888
棕发蓝眼
听来熟悉吗？
brown hair, blue eyes.
Sound familiar?

172
00:11:43,602 --> 00:11:47,800
如果黛维娜没和马赛尔在一起
他就不会知道我们在使用魔法
If Davina is not with Marcel,
he won't know if we're practicing magic.

173
00:11:47,973 --> 00:11:51,773
而如果我们可以找到她
一切都得以补救
And if we can actually get her back,
we can fix everything.

174
00:11:52,545 --> 00:11:56,709
太阳要下山了
会有更多吸血鬼出来找人
Sun goes down,
vampire search parties quadruple.

175
00:12:00,319 --> 00:12:02,913
我从她家的老房子里找到了这个
I got this from her family's old house.

176
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:06,080
应该可以施定位咒
Feel like a locator spell?

177
00:12:07,860 --> 00:12:09,327
继续喝
Keep drinking.

178
00:12:09,495 --> 00:12:12,589
你要让体内充满马鞭草
这样你就不会再被魅惑了
You need the vervain in your system
so you can't be compelled again.

179
00:12:12,765 --> 00:12:17,896
卡蜜
你家冰箱里有人血吗？
Hey, Cami, you don't have any, like,
human blood in your fridge, do you?

180
00:12:19,004 --> 00:12:20,596
