Promise you'll meet us
as soon as it gets dark out.

209
00:14:15,421 --> 00:14:18,447
好的，别担心我
别让他们找到你
Yeah, don't worry about me.
Just don't let them find you.

210
00:14:20,559 --> 00:14:22,550
