Everything is about to change.

218
00:14:49,722 --> 00:14:50,814
黛维娜溜出来了
Davina is on the loose.

219
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:53,185
你查得很清楚是吗？
Figured that out on your own, huh?

220
00:14:53,359 --> 00:14:55,793
但这跟我有什么关系呢？
Remind me again
why I should give a damn.

221
00:14:55,961 --> 00:15:00,057
我需要你的帮助
好让女巫们完成收种祭
I need something from you, so that
the witches can complete the Harvest.

222
00:15:00,232 --> 00:15:03,531
