00:22:18,737 --> 00:22:22,833
如果你真要这么做
就不要退缩
If you're gonna do it,
don't hold back.

325
00:22:24,710 --> 00:22:26,234
用你所有的力量对付他们
You hit them with all you got.

326
00:22:34,553 --> 00:22:38,353
真成人啊
你没告诉黛维娜如果她杀了克劳斯
That was very sweet, not telling Davina
that if she kills Klaus

327
00:22:38,523 --> 00:22:40,184
你也会死，真是太高尚了
you die, too.
Very noble.

328
00:22:41,026 --> 00:22:42,891
问题是，如果她真要去找我哥哥算帐
Problem is,
if she goes after my brother,

329
00:22:43,061 --> 00:22:45,120
死的人会是她
she'll be the one who ends up dead.

330
00:22:45,297 --> 00:22:49,597
这注定是个悲剧，送死也就没必要了
A very unnecessary end
to an already tragic story.

331
00:22:53,405 --> 00:22:55,270
或许你愿意助我一臂之力帮帮她
Perhaps you'd like to help me help her.

332
00:22:58,777 --> 00:23:00,074
蕾贝卡去哪了？
Where's Rebekah gotten off to?

333
00:23:00,245 --> 00:23:02,110
我倒不担心蕾贝卡
It's not Rebekah that
I'm concerned about.

334
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:04,373
你怎么确定黛维娜一定会来？
And how are you be so
certain that Davina will come?

335
00:23:04,549 --> 00:23:06,483
这么说会让别人以为你已经忘记了
One might think you've forgotten
what it's like to be in the grip

336
00:23:06,685 --> 00:23:09,848
深陷在疯狂的迷恋中不能自拔的感觉
她会来的
of an all-consuming infatuation.
She'll come.

337
00:23:10,021 --> 00:23:13,218
有必要搞得那么悲情吗，尼克劳斯？
Are the maudlin theatrics
absolutely necessary, Niklaus?

338
00:23:13,325 --> 00:23:15,850
有道理
(VlOLlN PLAYlNG)
It's a fair point.

339
00:23:16,027 --> 00:23:18,894
提摩西，能换首欢快点的曲子吗？
Timothy, play something
a little more upbeat, please.

340
00:23:19,231 --> 00:23:20,664
真是个好孩子
That's a good lad.

341
00:23:25,103 --> 00:23:27,367
派你去传个话，去得还真是久啊
Took you long enough
to spread the word.

342
00:23:27,539 --> 00:23:29,063
你见过他的夜行者吗？
Have you met his Nightwalkers?

343
00:23:29,241 --> 00:23:30,799
都不太灵光
Not the brightest assortment.

344
00:23:30,976 --> 00:23:33,069
不管怎样，我都办妥了
All that matters is I got it covered.

345
00:23:33,245 --> 00:23:36,271
黛维娜来了以后
你们俩要让我跟她谈
When Davina gets here, you two
need to let me do the talking.

346
00:23:36,448 --> 00:23:38,313
你会有机会的
Well, I'm sure you'll have your chance.

347
00:23:38,884 --> 00:23:40,249
你好，亲爱的
Hello, love.

348
00:23:41,853 --> 00:23:45,050
沉默是金，谢谢你，提摩西
Silence is golden, Timothy.
Thank you.

349
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,357
黛维娜？
Davina?

350
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:53,157
我已经来了，让他下来
You got me here.
Now let him down.

351
00:23:53,331 --> 00:23:56,698
我们得先谈谈关于你
回到我们身边的问题
Well, first, we have to have a little chat
about you returning to the fold.

352
00:23:58,236 --> 00:24:00,568
我怎么跟你说的，克劳斯
让我来
What did I say, Klaus?
I got this.

353
00:24:01,306 --> 00:24:02,739
小黛，发生什么事了？
D, what happened?

354
00:24:02,908 --> 00:24:03,966
你为什么要逃走？
Why'd you run?

355
00:24:04,443 --> 00:24:06,843
告诉我
我能帮你解决问题
Talk to me.
Hey, I can make it right.

356
00:24:07,012 --> 00:24:09,708
怎么解决？威胁我的朋友吗？
How, by threatening my friend?

357
00:24:09,881 --> 00:24:11,473
事实上那是我的主意
Actually, that was my idea.

358
00:24:11,650 --> 00:24:14,244
我很抱歉
有时我为了表明立场做得有点过火
Apologies. I've been known to go
too far to make a point.

359
00:24:14,419 --> 00:24:17,149
但这样确实很管用
But I do always get results.

360
00:24:19,124 --> 00:24:23,083
你装出一副很自信的样子
但我知道真相
You pretend to be so confident,
but I know the truth.

361
00:24:24,763 --> 00:24:27,288
你害怕大家看到你真正的一面
You're afraid everyone can see
what you really are.

362
00:24:29,301 --> 00:24:30,563
一头野兽
An animal.

363
00:24:38,243 --> 00:24:39,471
怪物
A beast.

364
00:24:44,249 --> 00:24:46,149
为何不让我们看看你的真面目呢？
Why don't you show us your real face?

365
00:24:54,159 --> 00:24:55,626
我受够你了
That's enough of you.

366
00:24:56,728 --> 00:24:59,891
黛维娜，你不必这么做的
Davina, you don't have to do this.

367
00:25:00,065 --> 00:25:01,123
你
You.

368
00:25:02,367 --> 00:25:05,768
你当着我的面欺骗了我
You looked me in the eyes
and lied to my face.

369
00:25:05,937 --> 00:25:07,962
假装你想要帮我
Pretended you wanted to help me.

370
00:25:08,139 --> 00:25:09,231
听我说
Listen to me.

371
00:25:09,407 --> 00:25:10,738
你自称是高尚的人
You call yourself the noble one,

372
00:25:10,909 --> 00:25:13,343
但却跟你弟弟一样是个杀人凶手
but you're a killer
just like your brother.

373
00:25:13,512 --> 00:25:15,810
一千年来，你以无辜人们的鲜血为食
For a thousand years,
you fed on innocent blood.

374
00:25:17,148 --> 00:25:18,581
让你试试被鲜血噎死的滋味如何
Why don't you choke on it?

375
00:25:31,363 --> 00:25:32,660
还有你
And you.

376
00:25:37,335 --> 00:25:39,360
我曾那么信任你
I trusted you.

377
00:25:39,538 --> 00:25:43,668
深爱着你
但你却只是利用我巩固你的势力
I loved you. But you were
just using me to stay in power.

378
00:25:43,842 --> 00:25:45,207
你根本不关心我
You don't care about me.

379
00:25:45,377 --> 00:25:46,605
你错了
You're wrong.

380
00:25:46,778 --> 00:25:49,804
当你败给克劳斯
你就把我当作战利品给了他
When you lost to Klaus,
you handed me over like some trophy.

381
00:25:50,916 --> 00:25:52,577
或许我该用铜锅煮了你
Maybe I should boil you in bronze.

382
00:25:52,751 --> 00:25:54,742
我关心你
I care.

383
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:57,081
我视你如己出
I took you in like
you were my own blood.

384
00:26:07,098 --> 00:26:08,292
不会吧，亲爱的
Come on now, love.

385
00:26:08,466 --> 00:26:10,331
别跟我说你信他这一套
Don't tell me you were falling for that.

386
00:26:11,937 --> 00:26:13,871
我们女孩们是不是该好好聊聊了？
Isn't it time for us girls
to have a chat?

387
00:26:18,877 --> 00:26:20,777
这真是让人印象深刻
Now, that is impressive.

388
00:26:20,946 --> 00:26:22,573
要我说，他们都罪有应得
And well-deserved, in my opinion.

389
00:26:23,515 --> 00:26:26,484
在你对付我之前
我有个惊喜给你
Now, before you turn on me,
I have a surprise for you.

390
00:26:31,089 --> 00:26:32,989
小约，你怎么来了？快走
Josh, what are you doing?
Get out of here.

391
00:26:36,561 --> 00:26:37,926
你要干什么？
What are you doing?

392
00:26:39,130 --> 00:26:41,792
如果我是克劳斯
我会将小约的头扭下来
Now, if I were Klaus,
I would rip Josh's head from his neck,

393
00:26:41,967 --> 00:26:44,765
喂给夜行者
这将是你朋友的下场
feed it to a Nightwalker, and
that would be the end of your friend.

394
00:26:48,807 --> 00:26:51,640
但伤害他人是男孩子才喜欢干的事
But hurting people is
such a boyish thing to do,

395
00:26:51,810 --> 00:26:54,574
就像克劳斯如何魅惑那位
屋顶上的提琴手
Iike how Klaus compelled
your fiddler on the roof.

396
00:26:54,746 --> 00:26:58,648
虽然我喜怒无常
但我绝对不像我哥哥
And, while I am many things,
I'm certainly not my brother.

397
00:26:58,817 --> 00:27:01,411
没事了，提摩西，你可以下来了
没人会伤害你的
It's okay, Timothy. You can come down.
No one is going to hurt you.

398
00:27:01,586 --> 00:27:03,486
他告诉我不能从横梁上爬下来
He told me I couldn't
climb down off this beam.

399
00:27:03,655 --> 00:27:05,452
那就别用爬的，傻瓜
Then don't climb, silly.

400
00:27:05,624 --> 00:27:07,751
我是这里唯一有脑子的吗？
跳啊
Am I the only smart one in the room?
Jump.

401
00:27:28,580 --> 00:27:32,243
黛维娜，这些你是怎么做到的？
Davina, did you do all that?

402
00:27:33,952 --> 00:27:35,419
我是怎么到这里的？
How did I even get here?

403
00:27:36,054 --> 00:27:37,885
我会解释的，我保证
I'll explain everything, I promise.

404
00:27:51,836 --> 00:27:53,565
你为什么这么做？
Why are you doing this?

405
00:27:53,738 --> 00:27:56,673
在我看来，你掌控着整个局势
Seems to me that
you're the one holding all the cards,

406
00:27:56,841 --> 00:27:58,832
但却不知道该相信谁
yet you don't know who to trust.

407
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:00,671
我向你证明了你可以相信我
I've just proven
that you can trust me.

408
00:28:00,845 --> 00:28:02,506
现在我想再告诉你一件事
Now I'd like to show you
one more thing.

409
00:28:02,981 --> 00:28:04,278
不会耽误很久
It won't take long.

410
00:28:05,116 --> 00:28:06,515
你可以带着你的朋友
You can bring your friends.

411
00:28:10,522 --> 00:28:13,491
苏菲，我把知道的都告诉你了
Sophie, I told you
everything that I found.

412
00:28:13,658 --> 00:28:17,094
你说他把她埋在了
两棵可爱的橡树苗之间
You said he buried her
between two lovely oak saplings.

413
00:28:17,262 --> 00:28:19,594
这已经是两百年前的事了
News flash, that was 200 years ago.

414
00:28:19,764 --> 00:28:21,095
它们现在早就是大树了
They're all just trees now.

415
00:28:21,266 --> 00:28:23,461
你想成为全能女巫，就继续找啊
You want to be the all-powerful witch,
keep looking.

416
00:28:23,635 --> 00:28:24,624
做个祷告
Say a prayer.

417
00:28:24,803 --> 00:28:27,033
有点信心
你可以的
Have a little faith.
You can do this.

418
00:28:27,572 --> 00:28:30,302
好吧
(CELL PHONE BEEPS)
Okay.

419
00:28:48,159 --> 00:28:50,150
拜托，请帮帮我
Please, please help me.

420
00:28:50,595 --> 00:28:52,324
我在努力做正确的事
I'm trying to do the right thing.

421
00:29:28,299 --> 00:29:32,395
别担心，他们不是真的死了
只是非常饿
Oh, don't worry. They're not really dead.
Just really hungry, and...

422
00:29:33,938 --> 00:29:35,428
这样说也不会好点的
And I'm not helping.

423
00:29:35,607 --> 00:29:39,065
你觉得我哥哥尼克很坏吗？
马赛尔算是得他真传了
You think my brother, Nik, is awful?
Marcel learned from the best.

424
00:29:39,244 --> 00:29:42,805
他就是这样对待背叛他的
他所谓的朋友
This is how he treats his
so-called friends who betray him.

425
00:29:42,981 --> 00:29:46,610
这里大部分可怜的家伙所做的
都不会比小约做的过分
Most of what these poor souls did
is no worse than what Josh did.

426
00:29:46,785 --> 00:29:48,844
拿提艾里来说吧
Take Thierry, for example.

427
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:50,988
他曾是马赛尔最信任的朋友
He was Marcel's most trusted friend.

428
00:29:53,291 --> 00:29:55,589
克劳斯设计让他
打破了马赛尔的一条规矩
Klaus tricked him into
breaking one of Marcel's rules.

429
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:59,355
马赛尔明知如此
还是把提艾里关在这里
Marcel knows this, and yet
he keeps Thierry locked in here

430
00:29:59,531 --> 00:30:02,227
日复一日地受折磨
day after day suffering.

431
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:03,799
真是疯了
This is insane.

432
00:30:05,970 --> 00:30:07,403
你为什么告诉我这些？
Why are you telling me this?

433
00:30:07,572 --> 00:30:10,837
因为你得知道你要对付的是谁
Because you need to know
who you're dealing with,

434
00:30:11,009 --> 00:30:12,499
谁是你可以信任的人
who you can trust.

435
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:18,913
嘿，嘿，没事的
Hey, hey.
It's gonna be okay.

436
00:30:19,083 --> 00:30:22,143
你不会有事的
I mean, you know,
you're gonna be all right.

437
00:30:23,588 --> 00:30:24,748
来
Here.

438
00:30:24,923 --> 00:30:26,356
喝点水吧
Drink something.

439
00:30:28,393 --> 00:30:31,191
黛维娜，你和我都被马赛尔和克劳斯
Davina, both you and
I have been lied to

440
00:30:31,362 --> 00:30:34,058
欺骗和利用了
and taken advantage of
by Marcel and Klaus.

441
00:30:34,232 --> 00:30:36,223
也许我们联手能够给他们小小的报复
Maybe together,
we can get a little payback.

442
00:30:43,074 --> 00:30:44,268
提姆？
Tim?

443
00:30:47,612 --> 00:30:48,806
是克劳斯
It was Klaus.

444
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:50,675
他逼我这么做的
He made me do it.

445
00:30:50,849 --> 00:30:53,511
我之前都不知道自己在做什么
直到我让你…
I didn't even know what I was
doing until I made you...

446
00:30:54,919 --> 00:30:56,284
让她什么？
Made her what?

447
00:31:00,058 --> 00:31:01,389
喝水
Drink.

448
00:31:05,463 --> 00:31:07,693
- 提姆？
- 克劳斯在水里下毒了
-Tim?
-Klaus poisoned the water.

449
00:31:08,066 --> 00:31:09,260
提姆？
Tim?

450
00:31:11,936 --> 00:31:13,028
黛维娜
Davina.

451
00:31:13,805 --> 00:31:15,033
不
Oh, no.

452
00:31:26,351 --> 00:31:27,716
卡蜜，你还好吗？
Cami, are you all right?

453
00:31:28,853 --> 00:31:30,252
今天吃饭了吗？
Did you eat today?

454
00:31:31,522 --> 00:31:32,989
你一定是昏过去了
Oh, you must have fainted.

455
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:38,222
是啊，或许我就是神秘地
被四个女巫弄昏了
Yeah, or I got mystically
cold-cocked by four witches.

456
00:31:38,997 --> 00:31:40,225
黛维娜在哪？
Where's Davina?

457
00:31:40,398 --> 00:31:42,366
你朋友马赛尔知道她在这里吗？
Does your friend, Marcel,
know she's here?

458
00:31:42,533 --> 00:31:44,000
卡蜜，我可以解释
Cami, I can explain.

459
00:31:44,836 --> 00:31:46,929
吸血鬼？女巫？
Vampires? Witches?

460
00:31:47,105 --> 00:31:50,370
我的哥哥，你的侄子，被女巫下了咒
My brother, your nephew,
hexed by a witch.

461
00:31:51,576 --> 00:31:52,770
你怎么能瞒着我？
How could you not tell me?

462
00:31:52,944 --> 00:31:55,037
这很复杂
It's complicated.

463
00:31:56,547 --> 00:31:58,242
有很多事情你不明白
There's a lot you don't understand.

464
00:31:58,416 --> 00:32:00,043
你对我隐瞒真相
You hid the truth from me.

465
00:32:00,218 --> 00:32:02,584
你让我相信西恩疯了
You let me believe
that Sean was crazy,

466
00:32:02,754 --> 00:32:05,882
我疯了
而不是告诉我真相
that I was crazy,
instead of telling me the truth.

467
00:32:06,057 --> 00:32:07,888
我是在保护你
I was protecting you.

468
00:32:11,496 --> 00:32:14,829
你也看到西恩的下场了
卡蜜，拜托
You saw what happened to Sean.
Cami, please!

469
00:32:14,999 --> 00:32:16,296
离我远点
Get the hell away from me.

470
00:32:16,467 --> 00:32:19,595
你和这个城市里其他的怪物一样坏
You are every bit as bad
as the other monsters in this city.

471
00:32:29,213 --> 00:32:31,238
是不是非常尴尬呢？
Isn't this monumentally awkward?

472
00:32:34,886 --> 00:32:36,183
蕾贝卡，你在哪？
Rebekah, where are you?

473
00:32:36,354 --> 00:32:39,585
我和黛维娜在一起，她快死了
都是因为你的背叛
I'm with Davina, and
she's dying because of your treachery.

474
00:32:39,757 --> 00:32:41,987
出于对马赛尔的尊重，我曾试着跟她谈
Well, I tried to talk to her,
out of respect for Marcel,

475
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:44,492
但她明确表示她不是我们的朋友
but she made it quite clear
she is not our friend.

476
00:32:44,662 --> 00:32:46,527
你若觉得她是你的朋友，我向你道歉
My apologies if you
thought she was yours.

477
00:32:46,698 --> 00:32:48,290
告诉我要怎么救她
Just tell me how to cure her.

478
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:49,933
吸血鬼的血没有用
Vampire blood isn't working.

479
00:32:50,101 --> 00:32:51,796
对，不会有用的
No. It wouldn't.

480
00:32:51,970 --> 00:32:56,407
我魅惑提姆给她喝下的毒药
是非常有效的
You see, the poison I compelled
Timothy to feed her is quite potent.

481
00:32:56,574 --> 00:32:58,474
她死只是早晚的问题了
It's just a matter of time for her.

482
00:32:58,643 --> 00:33:01,771
是他们俩，你这个残忍的混蛋
For both of them,
you diabolical bastard.

483
00:33:01,946 --> 00:33:03,538
他们还是孩子
They're children.

484
00:33:03,715 --> 00:33:05,410
我们本来可以公平地和她做交易
We could've dealt with her fairly.

485
00:33:05,583 --> 00:33:07,949
对于威胁我们的人，不用谈什么交易
There is no dealing with
those who threaten us.

486
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:10,952
黛维娜与我对立的那一刻开始
命运就已定
Davina sealed her fate
when she stood against me.

487
00:33:11,122 --> 00:33:13,386
这是她的选择，不是我的
This was her choice, not mine.
(CELL PHONE BEEPS)

488
00:33:23,935 --> 00:33:25,926
别这样
(CHUCKLlNG)
Oh, come on.

489
00:33:26,104 --> 00:33:29,198
你们指责我的恶臭真是势不可档
The stench of your judgment
is overwhelming.

490
00:33:29,374 --> 00:33:32,434
需要我提醒你们
黛维娜刚打败了我们吗？
Need I remind you that
Davina just bested the lot of us?

491
00:33:32,610 --> 00:33:34,669
我只是做了该做的
I did what had to be done.

492
00:33:36,814 --> 00:33:38,543
别担心，以利亚
Don't worry, Elijah.

493
00:33:38,716 --> 00:33:40,513
我还是一如既往可被挽救
I remain as redeemable as ever.

494
00:33:40,685 --> 00:33:42,414
所以你魅惑那个男孩去给黛维娜下毒
So you compelled that boy
to poison Davina

495
00:33:42,587 --> 00:33:44,452
都不问问我和马赛尔
without consulting Marcel or myself.

496
00:33:45,623 --> 00:33:47,591
你知道最糟糕的问题是什么吗？
You know what the worst part is?

497
00:33:47,759 --> 00:33:49,249
是你太容易被看穿了
It's that you're so predictable,

498
00:33:49,427 --> 00:33:52,487
我不得不与你哥哥结盟
我根本不喜欢他
I had to make an alliance with your
brother, who I don't even like.

499
00:33:58,369 --> 00:34:01,202
听你的口气
你似乎有什么事想跟我说
Judging by your expression,
you have something you'd like to share.

500
00:34:01,372 --> 00:34:02,999
你说对了
Damn straight, I do.

501
00:34:03,174 --> 00:34:06,735
基兰稍早打了电话给我
就在莎宾和其他女巫
I got a call from Kieran earlier,
right after Sabine and some witches

502
00:34:06,911 --> 00:34:09,072
对黛维娜下手之后
almost got their hands on Davina first.

503
00:34:11,949 --> 00:34:13,314
你好啊
Oh, hello.

504
00:34:15,686 --> 00:34:17,244
让我猜猜，保护咒吗？
Let me guess, protection spell?

505
00:34:19,490 --> 00:34:22,357
你觉得我会白白浪费能施魔法的一天
什么都不做吗？
You think I'd let a day where witches
can do magic pass by without one?

506
00:34:24,962 --> 00:34:26,725
她们本该都这么做的
They all should've done the same.

507
00:34:27,031 --> 00:34:28,293
是啊
Yeah.

508
00:34:30,701 --> 00:34:34,000
你违反了我的规矩，莎宾
我猜你的保护咒
You broke one of my rules, Sabine,
and I'm guessing that spell of yours

509
00:34:34,172 --> 00:34:36,106
应该是一次性的吧
is probably a one-time deal.

510
00:34:37,508 --> 00:34:39,305
我给你两个选择
I'll give you two choices.

511
00:34:39,477 --> 00:34:43,174
你可以立刻和你天人永隔的朋友相见
An immediate reunion
with your dearly departed friends,

512
00:34:43,347 --> 00:34:46,214
也可以为我的一个小女巫朋友
施同样的保护咒
or you can do that same spell
for a young witch friend of mine.

513
00:34:48,352 --> 00:34:50,684
你大概知道我在说谁
Yeah, you probably know
which one I'm talking about.

514
00:34:55,793 --> 00:34:58,819
所以你声称去看夜行者时
So, when you slipped away to
allegedly check on your Nightwalkers,

515
00:34:58,996 --> 00:35:01,487
其实是在与一名女巫共谋
you were, in fact,
colluding with a witch.

516
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,524
很聪明嘛
Very clever.

517
00:35:04,702 --> 00:35:06,260
我应该感到自豪
I suppose I should be proud.

518
00:35:06,437 --> 00:35:10,396
我是想确保万无一失
I just wanted to make sure
I had a failsafe just in case,

519
00:35:10,575 --> 00:35:13,442
正如以利亚所料，你开始露出本性
as Elijah expected,
you started acting like you.

520
00:35:13,611 --> 00:35:15,511
但这次你选择了与女巫结盟
Except that now you've
involved the witches,

521
00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:17,944
而据我所知
女巫一直是我们的敌人
who, last time I checked,
were enemy to us all,

522
00:35:18,116 --> 00:35:20,914
对于我们的家人和一切都是威胁
to everything we have,
and to our family.

523
00:35:21,085 --> 00:35:22,677
黛维娜就是马赛尔的家人，尼克劳斯
Davina is Marcel's family, Niklaus,

524
00:35:22,854 --> 00:35:25,687
但你居然想取她性命
难道你忘了这一点吗？
or did that somehow slip your mind
as you tried to take her life?

525
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:31,221
打给蕾贝卡
You will call Rebekah.

526
00:35:31,395 --> 00:35:33,329
告诉她黛维娜会恢复
You'll tell her that Davina will recover.

527
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,034
可惜那个男孩活不了了
I do wish the same could be said
for that boy.

528
00:36:00,224 --> 00:36:01,816
提姆
Tim.

529
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:04,154
提姆，提姆
Tim? Tim.

530
00:36:05,229 --> 00:36:06,958
提姆，提姆，醒醒
Tim, wake up.

531
00:36:07,131 --> 00:36:08,826
提姆，快醒醒
Tim, please wake up.

532
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:10,297
睁开眼睛
Open your eyes.

533
00:36:11,469 --> 00:36:12,766
不要啊，不要
No, no.

534
00:36:14,405 --> 00:36:15,929
快醒来
Please wake up.

535
00:36:18,109 --> 00:36:20,009
别丢下我一个人
Please don't leave me alone.

536
00:36:41,899 --> 00:36:43,059
她还好吗？
Is she okay?

537
00:36:44,936 --> 00:36:47,496
她情绪崩溃，疲惫不堪
She's devastated and exhausted.

538
00:36:50,641 --> 00:36:51,972
她的房间在哪里？
Where's her room?

539
00:36:52,143 --> 00:36:53,405
不用，我来就行
No, I got her.

540
00:36:56,147 --> 00:36:57,409
交给我吧
I got her.

541
00:37:28,379 --> 00:37:31,371
有人说，这是男人的世界
HAYLEY: It is said that
this is a man's world.

542
00:37:31,549 --> 00:37:33,141
有时候的确是这样
And sometimes it is.

543
00:37:41,926 --> 00:37:45,760
虽然很多木匣女孩被解救
但那毕竟是有限的
For every Casket Girl that was saved,
countless others were not.

544
00:37:46,430 --> 00:37:48,261
她永远不会再信任我了
She'll never trust me again.

545
00:37:48,466 --> 00:37:49,763
也许吧
Perhaps.

546
00:37:50,835 --> 00:37:53,269
但你永远不能放弃重新争取她的信任
You must never surrender
the fight to reclaim that trust.

547
00:37:54,305 --> 00:37:56,773
但女人其实比世人想像的更坚韧
HAYLEY: But women are more
resilient than given credit for.

548
00:37:58,542 --> 00:38:01,033
这些画，是什么？
These drawings, what are they?

549
00:38:02,647 --> 00:38:05,810
她在阁楼时就一直画这些
She drew those the whole time
she was in the attic,

550
00:38:05,983 --> 00:38:08,781
她感受到魔法时，画出来的就不一样
said they're different than what
she draws when she senses magic.

551
00:38:11,622 --> 00:38:13,317
这些，她称之为邪恶
These ones, she called them evil.

552
00:38:16,894 --> 00:38:19,124
而有些女人呢
HAYLEY: And some women,
well...

553
00:38:20,898 --> 00:38:23,492
这么说吧，曾欺压她们的人最好小心点
Let's just say, their oppressors
had better watch out.

554
00:38:34,512 --> 00:38:35,843
见到我很惊讶吗？
Surprised to see me?

555
00:38:36,013 --> 00:38:38,174
毕竟你曾魅惑我让我离开
After all, you did
compel me to leave town.

556
00:38:39,116 --> 00:38:40,276
你记得了
You remember.

557
00:38:40,451 --> 00:38:42,282
这都是解除魅惑的功劳
Chalk one up for de-compulsion.

558
00:38:42,453 --> 00:38:43,943
虽然痛得要死，不过很值得
Hurts like hell, but it's worth it.

559
00:38:44,155 --> 00:38:47,215
让我明白了为什么我想留下来
Made me realize exactly
why I want to stick around.

560
00:38:47,358 --> 00:38:51,886
对了，克劳斯，如果你再敢
伤害戴维娜和小约
And Klaus, if you hurt
Davina or Josh in any way,

561
00:38:52,063 --> 00:38:53,257
我会向全世界揭发你
I'll expose you to the world.

562
00:38:53,431 --> 00:38:55,831
你就可以跟法语区吻别了
And then, you can kiss
the French Quarter goodbye.

563
00:38:56,334 --> 00:38:57,596
永别
Forever.

564
00:38:58,169 --> 00:38:59,659
晚安了
Have a nice night.

565
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:04,440
我也很坚韧
HAYLEY: I, too, am resilient.

566
00:39:04,608 --> 00:39:07,702
我受够了被压迫
And I'm tired of being oppressed.

567
00:39:07,878 --> 00:39:10,904
一千年来，我哥哥为了他想要的东西
不择手段
For a thousand years, my brother has
taken what he wants,

568
00:39:10,348 --> 00:39:13,915
不计后果
in whatever way he wants,
regardless of the consequences.

569
00:39:14,085 --> 00:39:18,146
马赛尔似乎已经默许
而以利亚也一直陪伴在他身旁
Marcel seems determined to allow it,
and Elijah stands right by his side

570
00:39:18,322 --> 00:39:20,688
徒劳地等待着他某一天会改变
futilely awaiting
the day that he'll change.

571
00:39:27,198 --> 00:39:28,722
男人很混蛋
So, men suck.

572
00:39:29,767 --> 00:39:31,325
你想要我怎么做？
What do you want me to do about it?

573
00:39:32,269 --> 00:39:33,998
虽然你警告过马赛尔
Despite your dire warnings to Marcel,

574
00:39:34,171 --> 00:39:36,366
但他似乎无法放弃我哥哥
he just can't seem to quit my brother.

575
00:39:36,540 --> 00:39:38,235
他们肩并肩
The two of them stand side by side,

576
00:39:38,409 --> 00:39:41,037
统治着这个城市
却留你在这里腐烂
ruling this city
whilst you're left in here to rot.

577
00:39:43,681 --> 00:39:46,275
我希望你帮我夺回纽奥良
I want you to help me take
New Orleans right out from

578
00:39:46,450 --> 00:39:47,781
让他们眼睁睁看着
under all of their noses.

579
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:52,187
而且我有一个秘密武器
And I have something
they won't see coming,

580
00:39:52,356 --> 00:39:54,051
一个内应
someone on the inside.

581
00:39:55,226 --> 00:39:57,626
她自己也是个很坚韧的女孩
She's quite the resilient girl herself.

582
00:40:22,086 --> 00:40:23,383
你还好吗？
You okay?

583
00:40:24,588 --> 00:40:26,021
我现在好多了
I'm better now.

584
00:40:28,592 --> 00:40:29,820
你今天过得如何？
How was your day?

585
00:40:31,128 --> 00:40:32,459
棒极了
Killer.

586
00:40:36,267 --> 00:40:37,495
这些画是什么？
What's with the artwork?

587
00:40:37,668 --> 00:40:39,602
黛维娜的素描
Uh... Davina's sketches.

588
00:40:40,905 --> 00:40:44,033
不知道是不是代表着什么预兆
I wonder if they represent
some kind of premonition.

589
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,104
好了
Okay.

590
00:40:48,479 --> 00:40:50,470
似乎在暗示什么即将到来
They seem to suggest
something is coming.

591
00:40:55,052 --> 00:40:57,350
似乎是凶兆
Something sinister.

592
00:41:13,304 --> 00:41:14,601
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

593
00:41:15,573 --> 00:41:17,006
那不是…
Isn't that...?

594
00:41:21,545 --> 00:41:23,137
你好，莎莉丝特
Hello, Celeste.

595
00:41:43,033 --> 00:41:44,694
快点，苏菲，快接电话
Come on, Sophie, pick up.

596
00:41:45,169 --> 00:41:46,466
快点接啊
Pick up.

597
00:41:51,008 --> 00:41:55,445
片名：创始吸血鬼（第一季）

